1. On je rekao da će *predstaviti* svoju novu kolekciju na reviji. (He said he will *present* his new collection at the fashion show.)
2. Danas ću *predstaviti* svoj novi projekat na sastanku. (Today I will *introduce* my new project at the meeting.)
3. Molim te da mi se *predstaviš*. (Please *introduce yourself* to me.)
4. Kako biste *predstavili* svoju kompaniju u jednoj rečenici? (How would you *describe* your company in one sentence?)
5. Naša ambasadorka će *predstavljati* Srbiju na međunarodnom samitu. (Our ambassador will *represent* Serbia at the international summit.)
6. Njen glas će se *predstaviti* u prvom delu koncerta. (Her voice will *perform* in the first part of the concert.)
7. Učenici će *predstaviti* svoje projekte na školskoj izložbi. (The students will *display* their projects at the school exhibition.)
8. Želim da *se predstavim* kao novi član tima. (I want to *introduce myself* as a new member of the team.)
9. Kandidat će se *predstaviti* komisiji tokom intervjua. (The candidate will *present himself* to the committee during the interview.)
10. Pevač će *se predstaviti* novim singlom na radiju. (The singer will *promote himself* with a new single on the radio.)